    <node id="Region R">
      <data key="d0">Region R</data>
      <data key="d1">location</data>
      <data key="d2">Region R is an example of a location where large-scale investment in solar and wind energy has been made to reduce fossil fuel dependence and improve energy access.&lt;SEP&gt;Region R is mentioned as a location where significant investments in renewable energy sources improved energy access.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d92e720e7cfbfc2155b52aa88b0156f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba30ff765cf7628b7d0bf16fe4039b48</data>
