    <node id="Energy Poverty">
      <data key="d0">Energy Poverty</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Energy poverty is a significant concern affecting education, healthcare, and social development in many regions due to lack of energy availability.&lt;SEP&gt;Energy poverty refers to the lack of access to modern energy services, which affects quality of life and economic development, particularly in underprivileged regions.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-0d92e720e7cfbfc2155b52aa88b0156f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba30ff765cf7628b7d0bf16fe4039b48</data>
