      <data key="d0">Mitigation Strategies</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Mitigation strategies aim to reduce greenhouse gas emissions and include energy efficiency, carbon pricing, and investments in low-carbon technologies.</data>
